{"type":"message","id":"1d90e00e","parentId":"1767dc5c","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:31:56.831Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3AFB6A8DD89669F8B765\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"3EB011A25C41DB93D07E16\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"sender\": \"Gustavo Toledo\",\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Gustavo Toledo (+573183718246)\",\n  \"id\": \"+573183718246\",\n  \"name\": \"Gustavo Toledo\",\n  \"e164\": \"+573183718246\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"75806961324068@lid\",\n  \"body\": \"Necesito aprobación para revisar Gmail/Calendar con `gog`.\\n\\nEjecuta exactamente esto:\\n\\n`/approve allow-once powershell -NoProfile -Command \\\"$env:GOG_ACCOUNT='atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com';\\nWrite-Host '=== FORWARDED / IMPORTANT INBOX ===';\\ngog gmail messages search 'in:inbox (from:toledo970501@gmail.com OR subject:Fwd OR subject:RV: OR subject:FW: OR subject:Fwd:) newer_than:14d' --max 50 --account atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com;\\nWrite-Host '=== TODAY / DEADLINE KEYWORDS ===';\\ngog gmail messages search 'in:inbox (today OR hoy OR deadline OR vence OR vencimiento OR due OR due date OR challenge OR interview OR prueba OR test OR task OR pendiente OR reminder OR meeting OR reunión OR factura OR payment OR pago) newer_than:30d' --max 50 --account atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com;\\nWrite-Host '=== UNREAD INBOX ===';\\ngog gmail messages search 'in:inbox is:unread newer_than:14d' --max 50 --account atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com;\\nWrite-Host '=== CALENDARS ===';\\ngog calendar list --account atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com\\\"` \\n\\nEn cuanto lo apruebes, sigo.\"\n}\n```\n\nEsto no lo veo en las sesiones de atlas para poderlas copiar facil en mi pc"}],"timestamp":1774715516824}}
