{"type":"message","id":"8a225a17","parentId":"ff998166","timestamp":"2026-03-29T00:40:44.550Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Si te refieres a **Atlas**, hoy te quedan estas actividades claras:\n\n- **Aprobar en tu otra cuenta lo de Vercel**\n- **Confirmar si Ares sí movió lo del entrenamiento de hoy**\n- **Lo de la factura ya quedó resuelto por ahora**\n  - cálculo listo\n  - recordatorio mensual activo\n\nSi quieres, te lo reduzco a **top 3 de hoy** bien corto.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08605887b83f1aa90169c8750db2a08191a712cda028fd2cfc\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":49179,"output":98,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49277,"cost":{"input":0.12294750000000002,"output":0.00147,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.12441750000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774744838884,"responseId":"resp_08605887b83f1aa90169c8750b808c81919670b73f06f6d90b"}}
